Assessment prepared by: ReelSaga AppSec / Cyber Security Team
Application: ReelSaga Android (in.reelsaga.android)
Classification: CONFIDENTIAL — INTERNAL USE ONLY

PERMITTED USE
-------------
Authorized ReelSaga employees, contractors, and security auditors may use,
copy, and distribute this assessment package internally for:

  - Security remediation and engineering fixes
  - Compliance and audit documentation
  - Security awareness training (internal)

PROHIBITED USE
--------------
Without written approval from ReelSaga Innovations Pvt Ltd:

  - Public disclosure of extracted API keys, tokens, or live proof responses
  - Use of proof-of-exposure scripts against production systems outside
    authorized security testing windows
  - Redistribution of this package to third parties
  - Use of findings to attack ReelSaga users, infrastructure, or partners

PROOF-OF-EXPOSURE ARTIFACTS
---------------------------
Files under proof-of-exposure/ contain evidence that embedded credentials
can be abused. They are provided solely to demonstrate risk to the
development team. Tokens and refresh credentials in JSON responses must
be treated as sensitive and rotated after review.

NO WARRANTY
-----------
This assessment is provided "as is" for internal security purposes.
Static analysis may not reflect the current Play Store build.

